{"id": "ChIJbTB3bKKAhYAR8Yqc6dEIMbQ", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 2338, "displayName": {"text": "Souvla", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Hip haunt featuring roasted meat sandwiches & salads, plus Greek yogurt, beer & wine.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJbTB3bKKAhYAR8Yqc6dEIMbQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VE1UVlJTamw2WW1aWVVsbHFjbTR5TVRaVlkyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Souvla is a solid healthy option in Hayes Valley. The food quality is good and leaves you feeling light after, though the flavors are a bit mild. Great spot if you want something clean and quick. Don’t skip dessert—the Greek yogurt with baklava crumbs is a perfect guilt-free treat!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Souvla is a solid healthy option in Hayes Valley. The food quality is good and leaves you feeling light after, though the flavors are a bit mild. Great spot if you want something clean and quick. Don’t skip dessert—the Greek yogurt with baklava crumbs is a perfect guilt-free treat!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "vamsi C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110443144189514634250/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWEzWvALC0xMBO_V1DIJFSUf2ITEWirGRppX9zVLxb2_Ih9g09=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T21:47:34.724183464Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VE1UVlJTamw2WW1aWVVsbHFjbTR5TVRaVlkyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210VE1UVlJTamw2WW1aWVVsbHFjbTR5TVRaVlkyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580a26c77306d:0xb43108d1e99c8af1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbTB3bKKAhYAR8Yqc6dEIMbQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3MmF5MXFkbVUwY0dwcFMwMVdOVWQxTTBWalkyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Souvla was really really good. All the food was amazing. The salads were fresh and the feta you could tell was sprinkled on directly before they served it. The pita was soft. I would hope that it was easier to eat but other than that it was perfect. The food came really fast and when we got our Greek fries. They were very warm and you could tell they just came out of the fryer. The ranch was super good and if you stuffed the pita with any salad you get a bite of delicious comforting food. Will definitely come here again", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Souvla was really really good. All the food was amazing. The salads were fresh and the feta you could tell was sprinkled on directly before they served it. The pita was soft. I would hope that it was easier to eat but other than that it was perfect. The food came really fast and when we got our Greek fries. They were very warm and you could tell they just came out of the fryer. The ranch was super good and if you stuffed the pita with any salad you get a bite of delicious comforting food. Will definitely come here again", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Freya Kale", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114853577719616839249/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOx-ObauYeBMfJ9C-pMw7mfHFbu4AML2swgoEThggT711-SEw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-24T01:00:24.235804755Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3MmF5MXFkbVUwY0dwcFMwMVdOVWQxTTBWalkyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3MmF5MXFkbVUwY0dwcFMwMVdOVWQxTTBWalkyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580a26c77306d:0xb43108d1e99c8af1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbTB3bKKAhYAR8Yqc6dEIMbQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twZlEzTTFlRVZrYUhKWVR6Rk5WMVF6YlZZeGVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription":